    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and truly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, with every service record accounted for and performed on schedule. The exterior paint is flawless with no scratches or chips, and the interior is pristine, still retaining that new-car scent. Mechanically, it is perfect, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience that reflects its low mileage and superior care. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants a vehicle in showroom condition without any compromises.",
