    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a fantastic ride that\u2019s been truly well-loved? This beauty is in wonderful shape and runs like a dream. It\u2019s been my reliable companion, but it\u2019s ready for a new owner to take it on some fresh adventures! It's super clean, looks great, and is just waiting for a test drive. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
