    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This 2008 Corvette Z06 features the legendary LS7 7.0L small-block V8, delivering 505 hp through a Tremec TR-6060 6-speed manual transmission. The dry-sump lubrication system and titanium intake valves remain in excellent operating condition, ensuring high-RPM stability and oil pressure consistency. The hydroformed aluminum chassis provides superior torsional rigidity compared to the base C6, supported by a performance-tuned suspension and cross-drilled rotors for heat dissipation. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive fluid service and inspection of the limited-slip differential. While the vehicle exhibits minor aesthetic wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization, throttle response, and lateral grip remain sharp and uncompromised.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Ready for immediate sale.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
